			some info on how to get the word of allure :<BR>
<BR>
this is a rly rare word to get. you can have<BR>
it in doing a quest hehehehe. go in neriak foreign<BR>
quarters. go at the top of the first building. speak<BR>
with the 3 dark sisters. here is what u need to grab <BR>
for getting word of allure :<BR>
<BR>
- a charred wood wand (found in MistMoore)<BR>
- a Bloodstone (found easily in most of the cities)<BR>
- a charred pearl<BR>
- a charred ruby<BR>
<BR>
good luck on getting this word... look at all stores.<BR>
i personally found out the charred ruby at sal drana house<BR>
in neriak (foreign quarter).<BR>
Also a barbarian friend lvl30 told me that he found word<BR>
of allure on mommas mammoth in everfrost.<BR>
